					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpion451" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1918720); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1918720&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227303" alt="Scorpion451" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1918720)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpion451" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1918720); return false;" >Scorpion451</a></span> <span class="odate time_1421987040 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">23 Jan 2015 04:24</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2214384">
									

<p>The original Murphy's Law is that one should always assume that things will always happen the worst way that they possibly can. If things are allowed to go wrong, it is not bad luck but a failure to prevent the circumstances that allowed that situation to occur in the first place.</p>

