														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2215786">
									

<p>It's also not helpful to anyone if the proposed fixes aren't in any way relevant to the causes of these incidents, or could be reasonably predicted or accounted for.</p>
<p>&quot;You need to send the message earlier, using a more refined calculation.&quot;<br />
&quot;That wouldn't have helped, as the ship appeared later and in a different position than what our models predicted.&quot;<br />
&quot;So?&quot;</p>
<p>It's just spitting on the grave of researchers who died saying &quot;Here's what we think you <em>should</em> have done, but that doesn't matter because it wouldn't have helped anyways!&quot;</p>

